  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\nConnect `status-go` RPC for removing wallet accounts.\r\n\r\n### Depends on #18421\r\n\r\n#### RPC method: `accounts_deleteAccount`\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n- On confirmation, the RPC should be called with the address of the account to be removed\r\n- On successful removal, the toast with the message `Account has been removed` (`Watched address has been removed` for watched address) is shown\r\n- Call the `:wallet/get-accounts` event upon successful removal to refresh the accounts list\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Toast message is shown upon successful removal\r\n- The account is removed successfully with no listings in Wallet home, Account Switcher,...etc.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nThe default account can not be removed. \r\n",
